high_descs: turn left and walk to the fridge, then turn left and walk to the kitchen island counter
grab a knife off of the kitchen island counter
turn right and walk past the kitchen island to the sink at the far end of the room
cut up the tomato to the back right
place the knife inside the sink
grab a tomato slice out of the sink
move to the right a bit and face the kitchen counter again
place the slice of tomato inside a bowl on the kitchen counter to the right of the sink
pick up the bowl off of the counter
move over to the fridge to your right and face the fridge
place the bowl inside of the fridge there
anns.task_desc: place a bowl with a tomato slice in it inside the fridge

high_descs: turn around and move forward toward the right corner of the white table
pick up the knife with the yellow handle that is in front of the spoon
turn right and move forward to be in front of the kitchen sink
slice the tomato with the knife that is behind the apple in the back of the sink on the right side
put the knife into the sink between the apple and the tomato that is to the left of the apple
pick up the slice of the tomato
move to the right to face the counter that is to the right of the sink
put the slice of tomato into the clear bowl that is to the right of the sink
pick up the bowl with the slice of tomato
turn to the right and move slightly right to face the refrigerator
open the fridge door, put the bowl with the slice of tomato into the fridge on the top shelf and close the door
anns.task_desc: put a bowl with a slice of a tomato into the refrigerator

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the counter.
Pick up the knife in front of the spoon.
Turn to the right, walk to the sink.
Slice the tomato in the back of the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Step to the right of the sink.
Put the tomato slice in the bowl on the counter.
Pick the bowl up off of the counter.
Turn to the right, step in front of the fridge.
Put the bowl on the bottom shelf in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with a slice of tomato into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the table.
Pick up the big knife that is on the table.
Turn to the right and head towards the sink.
Stop in front of the sink.
Use the knife to cut a slice of tomato.
Pick up the slice of tomato.
Move to the counter directly to the right of the sink where the clear bowl is.
Put the slice of tomato in the clear bowl.
Pick up the clear bowl with the tomato in it.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the bowl inside, then close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with tomato in it inside the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the yellow knife on the table.
Pick up the yellow knife in front of the spoon on the table.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Cut up the tomato farthest away from you in the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Pick up a piece of tomato from the sink.
Walk to the glass bowl to the right of the sink.
Place the piece of tomato in the glass bowl.
Pick up the glass bowl from the counter.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the bowl in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass bowl with a piece of tomato in it into the fridge.
